OL,3,CGovernment apologises to DES drug
OL,4,Cvictims after ITV News investigation
OL,6,FITV News Social Affairs Correspondent
OL,7,FSarah Corker and Senior Producer
OL,8,FLottie Kilraine report
OL,10,FThe government has apologised to
OL,11,Fvictims of the DES drug scandal after
OL,12,Fa year-long ITV News investigation
OL,13,Fexposed the scale of the harm caused
OL,14,Fby the dangerous pregnancy drug, that
OL,15,Fwas prescribed to women on the NHS for
OL,16,Fdecades.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
