OL,6,F"It is only understandable that they
OL,7,Ffeel their healthcare system failed to
OL,8,Faddress this pattern of
OL,9,Fmultigenerational harm by inadequately
OL,10,Finforming people and protecting them
OL,11,Ffrom known harmful effects of DES."
OL,13,FCampaigners have welcomed today's
OL,14,Frecognition of their suffering and
OL,15,Fhope it may lead to improved
OL,16,Fhealthcare and awareness of DES.
OL,18,FJan Hall, 75, from Bournemouth, was
OL,19,Fpersonally named in the health
OL,20,Fsecretary's letter.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
