OL,6,FShe believes her mother Rita was
OL,7,Fprescribed DES during three
OL,8,Fpregnancies and that exposure
OL,9,Fcontributed to her death, aged 32,
OL,10,Ffrom breast cancer in 1951, when Jan
OL,11,Fwas a toddler.
OL,13,FShe has suffered a lifetime of health
OL,14,Fproblems, including a diagnosis of
OL,15,Fcervical cancer in her twenties.
OL,17,F"I feel that this apology is a huge
OL,18,Fstep forward after so many years of
OL,19,Fcampaigning, it makes it feel
OL,20,Fworthwhile," Jan told ITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
