OL,6,F"I think it was very difficult for the
OL,7,Fgovernment to have accepted this, but
OL,8,Fthe evidence is clear that for many,
OL,9,Fmany years they have avoided answering
OL,10,Fthe questions."
OL,12,FJan Hall, 75, from Bournemouth, was
OL,13,Fpersonally named in the health
OL,14,Fsecretary's letter and said the
OL,15,Fapology makes her campaigning feel
OL,16,F'worthwhile'
