OL,6,FJan's daughters have also had
OL,7,Fgynaecological problems, including
OL,8,Fabnormal smears and pre-cancerous
OL,9,Fcells in the cervix, but said doctors
OL,10,Faren't taking their concerns about DES
OL,11,Fseriously.
OL,13,FShe now fears for the future of her
OL,14,Fgrandchildren, as the generational
OL,15,Fimpacts of the drug are still under-
OL,16,Fresearched.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
