OL,6,F"It's a man-made disaster," she said.
OL,7,F"It wasn't intentionally done, but
OL,8,Fonce they knew the risks, it was
OL,9,Fcontinued to be used, and that is
OL,10,Fhorrendous."
OL,12,FJan's story prompted hundreds of women
OL,13,Fto contact us to share their own
OL,14,Fexperiences of being given the drug.
OL,16,FSince then, more than 300 victims have
OL,17,Fformed DES Justice UK, which launched
OL,18,Fin November.
