OL,6,FIt was Jan's MP Jessica Toale who has
OL,7,Fled calls for urgent action in
OL,8,Fparliament over the scandal, after
OL,9,Fhearing her constituent's story on ITV
OL,10,FNews.
OL,12,FIn July, she wrote a letter signed by
OL,13,F37 cross-party MPs to Health Secretary
OL,14,FWes Streeting calling on the him to
OL,15,Fformally apologise to victims and to
OL,16,Fcommit to enhanced cancer screenings
OL,17,Ffor those exposed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
