OL,6,FMs Toale told ITV News she believes
OL,7,FDES is "potentially one of the biggest
OL,8,Fpharmaceutical scandals we will ever
OL,9,Fhave seen in British history".
OL,11,FFour months on, the health secretary's
OL,12,Freply commits to doing more to raise
OL,13,Fawareness among health professionals
OL,14,Fabout the associated harms with
OL,15,Fexposure to the drug.
