OL,6,FThis is a significant moment in the
OL,7,Fcampaign for justice; however, the
OL,8,Fletter is carefully worded.
OL,10,FThe health secretary has acknowledged
OL,11,Fthe harm, but has not accepted
OL,12,Fliability.
OL,14,FOur investigation found that there
OL,15,Fwere warnings about the dangerous side
OL,16,Feffects of DES, but they were not
OL,17,Facted on for decades.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
