OL,6,FTheir daughters, known as DES
OL,7,Fdaughters, exposed in the womb, are at
OL,8,Fan increased risk of clear cell cancer
OL,9,Fof the cervix and vagina, which is not
OL,10,Fpicked up by routine screening.
OL,12,FDES Justice UK is now calling on Mr
OL,13,FStreeting to meet the campaigners to
OL,14,Fhear their stories first hand and
OL,15,Flaunch a full statutory public
OL,16,Finquiry, with clear recommendations
OL,17,Ffollowed by swift actions.
